snippet.title: BEAT DA BEAT GAMEPLAY TRAILER
snippet.description:
UPCOMING IN SUMMER 2015!

Hurrican-like Bullet Hell for mobile phones (iOS, Android, Windows Phone).
Avoid the bullet rain to the rhythms of dubstep! 
Help the hero to defeat the hordes of invaders and take revenge on the interstellar agressor!
